Fern Andra https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fern_Andra 0 Fern Andra, Dowager Baroness von Weichs (November 24, 1893 – February 8, 1974) was an American actress, film director, script writer and producer. Next to Henny Porten and Asta Nielsen she was one of the most popular and best-known actresses in German silent film.
